PEOPLE
v.
CURRY S237037 Supreme Court of California. SEPTEMBER 12, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 1/2. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for People v. Adelmann (2018) 4 Cal.5th 1071, 232 Cal.Rptr.3d 421, 416 P.3d 786, is hereby dismissed. ( Cal. Rules of Court, Rule 8.528(b).)
